title: For the 1st time ever, 8 spacecraft are docked to the International Space Station
description: All eight of the International Space Station's docking ports are currently occupied by visiting spacecraft, marking a milestone for crewed spaceflight.
content:
The space station is feeling like a lot of us in the wake of Thanksgiving — very, very full.
